I found a blog post here:
http://obakfahad.com/archives/a-very-beautiful-conky-with-rss-feed-reader

Which I used to start from. 
I don't know why it wasn't easier to get add an RSS feed reader to conky.
All I wanted was an RSS feed for github on my desktop. 
So I modified the one above.

